column5: Hello All  I have been veiwing the board for a while now and decided i should join. I am an avid fisherman and hunter. A few of my PB are already on this site i fish a fair bit with Bucktail.Just wanted to say here i am and i am looking forward to being apart of the OFC community.
welcome, enjoy and plz post some fish porn...
Agreed, nobody likes to go hunting for pictures. Feel free to add some pictures via photobucket and share with us some fishing stories!  Thanks for joining up, MTBF
Welcome aboard, man!  You must be brave if you joined at this time of year
Welcome to the site, look forward to some reports.
Welcome aboard. You're fishing with a dude who knows what he's doing.
Welcome to the board, look forward to seeing some posts with pics
Welcome to the site, it's true, we really like pics.
Welcome to OFC rthrbfsh Looking forward to reading your future reports!!! Leechman
